OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FA man murdered his wife before cutting
OL,7,Fup her body and paying a friend #50 to
OL,8,Fhelp dispose of her remains, a court
OL,9,Fhas heard.JNicholas Metson, now 28,
OL,10,Fstabbed 26-year-old Holly Bramley to
OL,11,Fdeath at their flat in Shuttleworth
OL,12,FHouse, Lincoln, in March last year.
OL,14,FMetson and his friend Joshua Hancock,
OL,15,F28, then in the village of Bassingham
OL,16,Fabout 10 miles away.
OL,18,FSome of her body parts have yet to be
OL,19,Ffound, Lincoln Crown Court heard.
