OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FThe court was told police were called
OL,7,Fto the couple's flat on 24 March last
OL,8,Fyear after concerns were raised for Ms
OL,9,FBramley's safety.
OL,11,FOfficers visited the following day but
OL,12,Fgot no response on the first two
OL,13,Foccasions they knocked at the door.
OL,15,FWhen Metson answered after their third
OL,16,Fattempt, he claimed not to know where
OL,17,Fhis wife was and said she had suffered
OL,18,Fmental health problems, self-harmed
OL,19,Fand subjected him to domestic abuse.
