OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FAn initial search of the flat revealed
OL,7,Fa strong smell of ammonia, blood-
OL,8,Fstained sheets and a saw.
OL,10,FProsecutor Gordon Aspden said when
OL,11,Fofficers returned the items had been
OL,12,Fmoved.
OL,14,F"The flat was searched but there was
OL,15,Fabsolutely no sign of Holly," he said.
OL,17,F"At one point Mr Metson joked she
OL,18,Fmight be hiding under the bed."
