OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FOn 25 March a member of the public
OL,7,Fnoticed a number of shopping bags
OL,8,Ffloating in the River Witham and
OL,9,Fexamined one of the bags.
OL,11,F"At this point he made a grim
OL,12,Fdiscovery," Mr Aspden told the court.
OL,14,F"At first he could not believe what he
OL,15,Fhad seen. He was looking at a severed
OL,16,Fhand."
OL,18,FPolice divers recovered 224 remains of
OL,19,FMs Bramley's body from the bags but
OL,20,Fparts of her heart, lungs and fingers
OL,21,Fwere still missing, the court heard.
