OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FIt took a pathologist over 13 hours to
OL,7,Fexamine all of her remains and the
OL,8,Fbody was so badly damaged they were
OL,9,Funable to establish the exact cause of
OL,10,Fdeath. However, she had suffered
OL,11,Fseveral stab wounds.
OL,13,FPolice later seized a set of garden
OL,14,Fpruners, two knives and a claw hammer
OL,15,Ffrom Metson's flat.
OL,17,F"In short, after murdering Holly he
OL,18,Fdestroyed her," Mr Aspden said.
