OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FAfter Killing his wife, Metson
OL,7,Fwithdrew #50 from Ms Bramley's bank
OL,8,Faccount and also made a number of
OL,9,Fsuspicious internet searches,
OL,10,Fincluding "what benefits do I get if
OL,11,Fmy wife has died?" and "can someone
OL,12,Fhaunt me after they die?"
OL,14,FCCTV footage recovered by police
OL,15,Fshowed Metson moving bags from his
OL,16,Fflat.
OL,18,F"They were carried by hand and also
OL,19,Fusing a Morrisons shopping trolley,
OL,20,Fand then conveyed to his yellow
OL,21,FPeugeot car," Mr Aspden said.
