OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,F"The most likely scenario is that Mr
OL,7,FMetson murdererd Holly in the bedroom,
OL,8,Fdismembered her body in the bath, and
OL,9,Fthen stored her body in the kitchen
OL,10,Flarder, before bagging her remains up."
OL,12,FEvidence from Metson's mobile phone
OL,13,Fshowed he had offered Hancock money
OL,14,Ffor a job during the early hours of 25
OL,15,FMarch.
OL,17,FThe next day a message on Hancock's
OL,18,Fphone said: "Just got #50 for
OL,19,Fdisposing of a body."
