OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FThe court Metson and Ms Bramley had
OL,7,Fbeen together since 2016 and married
OL,8,Fin 2021. Both had attended a support
OL,9,Fgroup for people with special needs.
OL,11,FMr Aspden said: "Mobile phone messages
OL,12,Fin the days leading up to the murder
OL,13,Findicate that by the start of 2023 the
OL,14,Fmarriage had broken down irretrievably
OL,15,Fand they were on the verge of
OL,16,Fseparating."
OL,18,FIn a statement Ms Bramley's mother
OL,19,FAnnette Bramley described Metson as an
OL,20,F"evil monster".
