OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FShe told him he had subjected her
OL,7,Ffamily "to a life sentence of grief."
OL,9,F"The heinous way in which she was
OL,10,Fmurdered and dismembered has left us
OL,11,Fin such unimaginable pain," Mrs
OL,12,FBramley told the court.
OL,14,FShe said Metson's controlling and
OL,15,Fcoercive behaviour had left the family
OL,16,Funable to see her dughter in the years
OL,17,Fbefore her death.
OL,19,FMetson had previously denied Ms
OL,20,FBramley's murder but last month.
