OL,3,C'Monster' who dismembered wife paid
OL,4,Cfriend #50 to help dump body
OL,6,FHe admitted conspiracy to pervert the
OL,7,Fcourse of justice by disposing of Ms
OL,8,FBramley's body.
OL,10,FHancock, of Walnut Close, Waddington,
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to obstructing a
OL,12,Fcoroner.
OL,14,FBoth are due to be sentenced on Monday.
